      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was conducted on the non-cannulated screw-rod-block assembly. Stiffness QoI changed by 0.9% between medium and fine mesh; yield force changed by 1.4%. Richardson extrapolation confirmed asymptotic convergence. Production mesh (approximately 420 000 hexahedral-dominant elements) adopted as baseline."
