      "rationale": "All nonlinear load steps achieved force and displacement residual norms below 1e-7. Maximum contact penetration observed was 0.003 mm against a minimum element edge of 0.18 mm (1.7%). One load step required bisection; final converged solution accepted. No hourglassing or element distortion warnings were flagged."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
